# Custom Briefing Module for Perfex CRM

![Perfex CRM Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Perfex%20CRM-v2.8.0-brightgreen.svg)

## Description

This is a custom module for Perfex CRM that adds a custom briefing tab to client profiles. The module allows you to gather information from clients based on a set of predefined questions.

## Features

- Add a custom briefing tab to client profiles.
- Gather important information from clients using predefined questions.
- Seamless integration into the Perfex CRM interface.

## Installation

1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Upload the "custom_briefing" folder to the "modules" directory of your Perfex CRM installation.
3. Go to the "Setup" section in your Perfex CRM admin panel.
4. Click on "Modules" and then on "Available Modules".
5. Find the "Custom Briefing" module and click "Install".
6. Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the installation.
7. During installation, the module will automatically create the necessary database table.

## Usage

1. After installation, open a client's profile.
2. You'll find a new "Briefing" tab where you can answer the predefined questions.

